{"id":589253,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/【立此存照】北京旅游想买纪念品？请买雾霾北/","date":"2018-07-14T23:14:56Z","modified":"2018-07-15T01:09:14Z","title":"【立此存照】北京旅游想买纪念品？请买”雾霾北京“雪花球！","content":"<p>【编者按】7月14日，记者Joanna Chiu (@joannachiu）在个人推特上发了一段雪花球小视频。与普通圣诞节雪花球不同，摇动这个雪球后，球中出现的不是纷纷落下的“雪花”，而是——雾霾。Joanna Chiu评论道：雾霾北京雪花球，完美纪念品！而另一位记者B. Allen-Ebrahiiman（@BethanyAllenEbr）注意到，雪球中的景致是CCTV大厦。该建筑常被人们戏称作“大裤衩”。她认为，这个雪球或许是某种微妙的政治讽刺。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Beijing smog globes. The perfect keepsake. <a href=\"https://t.co/kCpeFr8FZu\">pic.twitter.com/kCpeFr8FZu</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Joanna Chiu 趙淇欣 (@joannachiu) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/joannachiu/status/1018104151492812800?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 14, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">And isn’t the building inside the globes the CCTV building often mocked as the “split pants” building? Somehow I feel this is a subtle political commentary&#8230;. <a href=\"https://t.co/Jz52HTXa6A\">https://t.co/Jz52HTXa6A</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; B. Allen-Ebrahimian (@BethanyAllenEbr) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BethanyAllenEbr/status/1018248925415968768?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 14, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>中国数字时代的编辑在网络搜素了“雾霾北京雪花球”相关信息。</strong><strong>发现同款雪球在一家名为“哈比工坊”的公司有售。</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_589256\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/哈比工坊.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-589256\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/哈比工坊-300x138.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"253\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/哈比工坊-300x138.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/哈比工坊-768x353.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/哈比工坊-1024x471.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><a href=\"http://www.happysouvenirs.com/zh-hans/product/snow-globe-souvenirs-beijing\">哈比工坊网站</a>对雾霾北京雪花球的介绍</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>网站介绍写道：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>旅游纪念品是具有地方特色、富有纪念意义的旅游商品。雾霾是外界对北京的印象之一，这款旅游纪念品雪花球是浓缩了北京的一个天气特点，既有内涵，又让人忍俊不禁。设计方面：底座上主要元素新旧结合，围绕着北京作为这帝都地标性建筑、现代化建筑著名景点组成；内景 是中央电视台新办公楼建筑为主体，搭配小轿车，雪花是仿雾霾颜色，用手摇动后，会在建筑上、车上留下很多沙尘的效果（下图）。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_001-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-589254\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_001-1-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_001-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_001-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_001-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_001-1-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_001-1-50x50.jpg 50w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_001-1.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_002.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-589255\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_002-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_002-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_002-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_002-768x768.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_002-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_002-50x50.jpg 50w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/pic_002.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p></blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>据公司网站介绍：&#8221;哈比工坊是东莞市哈比工艺礼品有限公司的自有品牌，成立于2007年，是一家专业从事旅游纪念品，高端商务礼品赠品的开发设计和制造商，我们长期优势生产各种多功能音乐水晶球雪花球树脂水球和各类材质冰箱贴磁性贴及小摆件。欢迎订做、批发。&#8221;</p>\n","author":1056,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[9729,22350,10510,17623,21943,27145]}